Electrical  and Chilled Water meter readings - University of Central Florida (UCF) (2017-2018)

This dataset was scraped from https://www.oeis.ucf.edu/buildings and compiled for the purpose of the ASHRAE Energy Prediction competition. These are test (Ground Truth) labels that lower public LB directly. There is a building_id, timestamp, meter, and meter_reading column to merge directly onto test submission file.
